mong you?\u201d They said, \u201cThe one who is killed in the way of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIf that were so, there are few martyrs in my nation.\u201d They said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32727,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/09\/martyrs-protected-pain-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":38826,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Shahid: Martyrs protected from pain of death","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe martyr does not feel the pain of being killed except as one of you feels the pinch of an insect bite.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1668 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31702,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/02\/souls-of-martyrs-green-birds\/","url_meta":{"origin":38826,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Shuhada: Souls of martyrs alive in green birds of Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ka\u2019b ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace 